name: Sei Staked fastUSD
description: Powered by Elixir, sfastUSD is the yield-bearing staked version of fastUSD, a stablecoin integrated with core applications on Sei Network. sfastUSD is wholly backed by Elixir's deUSD, with crosschain transfers being powered by Hyperlane and pricing data secured by Redstone oracles deUSD holders on mainnet or alternative stablecoin holders on Sei Network can now access native yield, Elixir potion rewards, and liquid Sei rewards for holding (and using) Staked fastUSD (sfastUSD) within the ecosystem
